	<h2>
			Cláudio Guerra liga coronel à morte de Zuzu Angel		</h2>








        <div style="clear:both;"></div>
        <div class="itp-share">

                	<a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://cnv.memoriasreveladas.gov.br/outros-destaques/506-claudio-guerra-liga-coronel-a-morte-de-zuzu-angel.html" data-text="Cl&aacute;udio Guerra liga coronel &agrave; morte de Zuzu Angel" data-via="" data-lang="pt" data-size="small" data-related="" data-hashtags="" data-count="none"><img src="file://///mecsrv01/portalmec_dev/www/cnv/site/templates/cnv/images/btn_twitter.png" />Tweet</a><div class="itp-share-fbl">
